4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior knowledge. The program lasts 16 weeks with three live online classes per week, emphasizing foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration. Students will gain expertise in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence, as well as risk management through data loss prevention (DLP) strategies and compliance with international standards. Class sizes are limited to 16 participants, and graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Courses are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop